          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've been dreaming about launching a US-based company but the paperwork felt overwhelming, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bizee.com",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " just made that dream significantly easier. With over 200,000 entities formed and a stack of fresh features rolled out this year, the platform has quietly become one of the smartest ways to get your LLC, C-Corp, S-Corp, or nonprofit off the ground — without draining your startup budget.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent the past few weeks digging into what's new at Bizee, and honestly, the updates are impressive. Let me walk you through everything.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
