      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Bizee.com Actually Does (And Why 200K+ People Trust It)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://bizee.com"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bizee.com",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " handles the messy legal side of starting a business in the United States. We're talking formation documents, state filings, registered agent services, EIN applications — all the stuff that makes most entrepreneurs want to close their laptop and take a nap.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://bizee.com/business-formation"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But here's the thing that sets Bizee apart from a generic filing service: they've built a full ecosystem around business formation. You don't just get a piece of paper saying your LLC exists. You get ongoing compliance support, a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "registered agent for your first year completely free",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and access to tools that help you actually *run* the business after you form it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The numbers back this up. Over 200,000 entities have been created through the platform, and the reviews on Trustpilot consistently highlight three things: speed, transparency, and responsive customer support. For anyone who's dealt with state bureaucracy before, that combination is pure gold.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
