        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New Features Worth Getting Excited About",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bizee didn't just rest on their reputation. They've shipped several meaningful updates recently that deserve attention:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced Trademark Registration Service",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://bizee.com/business-formation/trademark-registration"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One of the biggest pain points for new business owners is protecting their brand name. Bizee now offers a streamlined ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "trademark registration process",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that walks you through federal filing with the USPTO. Instead of hiring a separate IP attorney (which can cost $1,000+), you can handle it right inside the same dashboard where you formed your LLC.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Business License Research Package",
            "marks": []
          }
