      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l8",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://bizee.com/articles/legal/choosing-a-business-structure"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 1: Choose your entity type.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " LLC, C-Corp, S-Corp, or nonprofit. Each structure has different tax implications and liability protections. If you're unsure, Bizee's ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "guide on choosing a business structure",
            "marks": [
              "l8"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " breaks it down in plain English.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Pick your state.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You can form in any US state, not just where you live. Wyoming, Delaware, and Nevada are popular for their business-friendly laws, but Bizee helps you figure out what makes sense for your situation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Provide basic details.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Company name, members/managers, address, and business purpose. The interface guides you through each field.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Select add-ons.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " This is where those new features come in — registered agent, EIN, virtual address, DBA, trademark filing. You can start lean and add services later.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Bizee files everything.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " They handle the state paperwork, follow up on any issues, and deliver your completed documents. Most formations wrap up in a few business days, though timing varies by state.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l9",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?mid=88819&id=2061927"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The whole experience feels like having a knowledgeable friend who's done this a thousand times walk you through it. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can explore the full formation process here",
            "marks": [
              "l9"
            ]
