      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The base LLC formation package is genuinely affordable — we're talking significantly less than what a local attorney would charge for the same paperwork. And that free first year of registered agent service? That alone saves you $100-$150 compared to buying it separately.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What I appreciate most is the transparency. There are no hidden upsells that ambush you at checkout. The add-ons are clearly priced, clearly explained, and completely optional. You can form a basic LLC and walk away happy, or you can build a full suite of services depending on what your business actually needs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For founders bootstrapping their first venture, this kind of cost structure matters enormously. Every dollar you save on formation is a dollar you can spend on product development, marketing, or your first hire.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
