      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bizee offers LLC formation at a competitive base price, plus state filing fees which vary by state. The first year of registered agent service is included free. Additional services like EIN filing, virtual address, and trademark registration are available as optional add-ons with transparent pricing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can non-US residents form a business through Bizee?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Bizee handles formations for international founders, including LLCs and C-Corps. You don't need to be a US citizen or have a US address. The platform guides non-residents through the EIN application process as well.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
