        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What's included in the free registered agent service?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your first year of registered agent service comes at no extra cost with Bizee formation packages. This includes receiving legal documents and official state correspondence on behalf of your business, with mail forwarding and compliance notifications. After the first year, you can renew at a standard annual rate.",
